(Photo by gotpap/Bauer-Griffin/GC Images) Photo: Gotpap/Bauer-Griffin, Getty Images Image 37 of 37 Kim Kardashian: 35 fashion looks for her 35th birthday 1 / 37 Back to Gallery Socialite turned reality star (...turned sex tape star ... turned business woman ... turned Playboy model ... turned mom ... turned global icon ... turned who-the-heck-knows-what-next) Kim Kardashian turns 35 on Wednesday.
Whether you love her or you hate her – and you've got to pick one because you can't in all honesty say you've never heard of her – has made a lot of interesting fashion choices over the years.
From the leather and jeans look of the 1993 Jenner family portrait (who several family members probably wish never happened) to the more recent West family photos with hubby Kanye , Kim has never failed to drop jaws – sometimes for good, and sometimes for bad.
Take a decade/pregnancy/career/husband-spanning look at Kim Kardashian's fashion choices in these photos.
